{"tid":1145966,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【首次夫妻檔現身】未諗追第3胎 鍾嘉欣擬教子女「求生技能」","createTime":"2019-05-09T03:08:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-09T07:01:12.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"ed559df7c24306fac9512189c77ae811d380bdc2","tid":1145966,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T03:08:31.000Z","msg":"甄子丹與太太汪詩詩、鍾嘉欣、蔡雪瑩、趙哲妤、湯君慈及湯君耀今晚盛裝現身尖沙嘴，出席頒獎典禮。<br />\n鍾嘉欣與老公Jeremy Leung首度一齊出席公開活動，身上所穿的是老公為她挑選的旗袍，未知是否太滿意太太的旗袍造型，二人合照時不時情深對望，Jeremy的手更在嘉欣臀部游走。嘉欣指04年華姐後未穿過旗袍，今次是相隔15年再穿。<br />\n嘉欣又透露今年母親節將在港度過，未知老公及子女打算如何慶祝，應該都是食飯，而囡囡每日都愛畫卡，所以她每日都收到囡囡的卡。至於囝囝近日學識爬，只要少看兩秒便消失在視線範圍，她說：「佢爬咗去仲要拎我哋啲拖鞋咬。」<br />\n提到經已湊夠「好」字，會否再生第三胎？她說：「唔會啦，暫時好好照顧兩個小朋友先，地球上生活唔容易，好多挑戰，等我同老公教晒所有武器畀佢哋生存用。」她坦言親自教會困身及花時間。<br />\n至於身為活動大使的子丹夫婦，多年來身體力行支持活動。提到母親節將至，詩詩表示一對子女每年都會送卡，她說：「個囡大啲，舊年帶埋婆婆出街，揀耳環送畀我，拎自己零用錢買。」問到子丹可會加囡囡零用錢讓她多些預算買禮物？子丹笑說：「財政大權喺媽咪度，加budget我都要申請。」<br />\n每年有情人節、母親節、結婚周年及生日等多個節日慶祝，子丹都會悉心為太太準備禮物及慶祝，更加是從沒有記漏日子，身旁的詩詩都不禁大讚子丹在這方面做得出色，問到詩詩可有記漏慶祝？子丹笑說：「唔係唔記得，係唔做，有時食餐飯慶祝。」詩詩即笑指日日都是節日。<br />\n子丹覺得太太平日忙於照顧屋企及處理公司事務，他應該在這方面下心思，他坦言要絞盡腦汁，總會遇到心思乾塘時，惟有誠意補救。詩詩再提到子丹今年為她安排的生日驚喜派對，子丹感激一眾好友保守秘密，令一向精明的太太事前察覺不到。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190508/large/1557328019_ee47.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190508%2Flarge%2F1557328019_ee47.jpg&h=cfec934d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190508/large/1557328016_758c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190508%2Flarge%2F1557328016_758c.jpg&h=4602aafd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190508/large/1557328016_f911.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190508%2Flarge%2F1557328016_f911.jpg&h=5eae0a77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190508/59579473\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190508%2F59579473&d=fyMqA0bs77BZF9qEbHCyftE6lK5ze4L1B2G6UiHaG78%3D&h=70ee7c38\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190508%2F59579473&h=eb32b993\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190508/59579473</a>"},{"pid":"8c99a61c760d46e3c37df85adf11dd340cd499d2","tid":1145966,"uid":173631,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T03:10:11.000Z","msg":"佢老公好撚柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ec78e241c9b67b3fadd203dc47c25043ac50830","tid":1145966,"uid":9707,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T03:11:00.000Z","msg":"It will kill"},{"pid":"211bf1cbccca4c469a7997eebf7534dc3680e843","tid":1145966,"uid":76463,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T03:12:07.000Z","msg":"有d嘔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e68b56ce02321ebc76e0816ae2880d1da1cdb206","tid":1145966,"uid":179967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c99a61c760d46e3c37df85adf11dd340cd499d2","tid":1145966,"uid":173631,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T03:10:11.000Z","msg":"佢老公好撚柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T03:17:39.000Z","msg":"金鐘連登仔.jpg"},{"pid":"b73a7944622325be5e1521aa5ab99669cb319ebb","tid":1145966,"uid":40272,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T03:28:04.000Z","msg":"求生技能 係咪搵個有錢佬 打開雙腳 夾到中出 下半世憂？"},{"pid":"4d14565919eb065fc11913c3676e03adff72c7c4","tid":1145966,"uid":55309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T03:29:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/lhBcgJ-NyZI\" data-sr-url=\"h